 could see a sleeker design with the hose running to the inside of the caliper.When Shimano introduced Dura-Ace 9000 mechanical, it’s safe to say it changed the way people viewed Shimano’s mechanical drive trains. The shifting was incredibly light and crisp, and provided some serious competition to the company’s own electronic groups. That same light action shifting made its way down to Ultegra, and now 105. The 5800 series borrows the compact lever shape of its more expensive siblings with shorter shift strokes that deliver what Shimano calls the “lightest and easiest front shifting Shimano has ever made. ” Like the rest of the group, shifters will be available in black or silver and include the same polymer coated shift cables from Ultegra 6800.Over the past year Shimano has created the awesome si.shimano website and has removed most of the printed manuals from the component boxes. The info on the si site is really good and well worth the read when it’s your first time installing a new component. Using the dealer manual (“DM” on the website) the installation was very straight forward, however I do have a lot of experience with Shimano’s hydraulic mountain bike brakes.The shape of the levers is very similar to the other Shimano Sora-Ace Di2 levers and is narrower through the body than the equivalent mechanical version. The R785 lever extends upwards more at the ‘point’ but not nearly as much as the SRAM hydraulic lever, and in real-life the lever looks far less bulbous than it does in photos.--------------------------3줄 해석 : 시마노는 로드용 디스크 브레이크 컴포넌트 세트를 듀라에이스 상위카테고리로 만들고 싶어한다mtb에서 XT급의 브레이크 성능을 가진 브레이크를 채용하며 그룹셋 이름은 kuroshio 가 될 예정이다.울테그라 급에도 디스크를 채용할 예정이며 이름은 Sora-ace가 될 예정이다.당연히구라지'),(5995,1405439,'자갤럼','스캇 쩌네.. 타기업이랑 비교가안됨..','\nGT.후지..프렘절단이든 포크절단이든 나몰라라하는데 스캇은  미국에서 딱 한대. 스템인지 핸들바인지 절단됬다고 8000대 리콜조치하넴.. 이정도 서비스정신은 있어야되지않음?'),(5996,1405440,'우끼끼','비온다고 자전거 안타는새끼들 극혐','\n진성 자덕이 아님자전거가 사람을타는사람'),(5997,1405441,'Set - go!','낼서군형벙에서 나눔한다','\n가장못생긴사람한테줌아..내가가져갔다가 내가가져오겠네